replies.body:
k well i read the whole list so don't think i get fearful easily, these are just phobias that bother me alot :P
Necrophobia – fear of death and/or the dead (anything that has to do with death to like ways of dying, hospitals, aging, and blood.)
Taphophobia, taphephobia – fear of the grave, or fear of being placed in a grave while still alive
Atychiphobia, kakorrhaphiophobia – fear of failure
Cleithrophobia – fear of being trapped
Enochlophobia - fear of crowds
Socialphobia - fear of other people or social situations #sociallyakward
